query:
SELECT c.id, c.reference_number, c.compensation_amount, c.commission_amount, c.net_payout_amount, 
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM passengers p WHERE p.claim_id = c.id) as passenger_count
FROM claims c 
ORDER BY c.id DESC 
LIMIT 10;
